{
  "stem": "894.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I'm going to visit my friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, well, why would you want to visit a Jewish girl, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess I was afraid to tell him that I am, too, so I just said, well, I like her, and so I want to visit her, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when we were in the ghetto already, they were hanging around and took over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a building in the back of the courtyard with a mother and a daughter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave them one room, and they took over the rest of the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were always around and always trying to make conversation, and, uh-- you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were-- I don't remember them being rude or coming into our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were everywhere, and so that was enough to feel uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the ghetto you talked about people having to move into other houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did anybody come to move into your house?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't, because I guess there wasn't that much room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, definitely our community, because by the time they came to our city, there-- every other city was already taken over by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and they took-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took everybody from their own homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every city had their own ghetto, and they took them from their own homes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing was, they-- they-- I think I will take a little bit of this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS] They-- some Polish, from Poland-- like I said, there was some people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in the city.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had come to escape, and they probably wound up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what happened was, sometime-- when they started-- before they started to take away the Jews, they took away people who didn't have Hungarian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the Polish people were taken away first.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
